Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.36,0:01:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事的 千香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.77,0:01:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.27,0:01:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.44,0:01:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会回来的 一定会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.87,0:01:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.45,0:02:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十四话 葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.19,0:02:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么就走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.93,0:02:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.00,0:02:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵、葵小姐 为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.68,0:02:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请带我们去 樱庭家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.55,0:02:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的要去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.99,0:02:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 和薰少爷一起决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.82,0:02:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 昨晚决定的 准备好好地谈一谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.07,0:03:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰挺没用的 不会自己骗自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.95,0:03:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 这就是薰的优点呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.76,0:03:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神乐崎 你来解释一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.26,0:03:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 主人 实际上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.23,0:03:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父亲大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.07,0:03:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿雅只是听从了我想和薰少爷见面的任性想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.74,0:03:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这完全是我的责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.51,0:03:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,判断由我来下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.35,0:03:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿雅小姐没有错 是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.45,0:03:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.29,0:03:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请原谅我突然的拜访
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.79,0:03:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 有些事 无论如何都想说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.50,0:03:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你闭嘴 这是樱庭家的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.13,0:03:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 父亲大人 请听一听薰少爷的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.90,0:04:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这也是葵的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.00,0:04:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想法？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.17,0:04:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请听一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.61,0:04:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有必要听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.34,0:04:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.28,0:04:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学长是个直率的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.32,0:04:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以觉得有点令人感到耀眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.33,0:04:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当我看着这样的学长 总觉得自己必须努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.40,0:04:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.07,0:04:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请听我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.57,0:04:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也求您了 无论如何 请听一听薰少爷的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.01,0:04:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要多嘴 神乐崎 搞清楚自己的立场！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.51,0:04:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是负责葵小姐教育的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.98,0:04:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵小姐的幸福 就是我的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.35,0:04:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了 请说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.86,0:04:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母亲大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.96,0:04:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.23,0:05:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我 现在的我 已经不是花菱家的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.34,0:05:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,与那时的立场不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.84,0:05:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在只是个普通的大学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.25,0:05:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,将来也没有什么保障
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.65,0:05:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 但是 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.65,0:05:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还以为你会说些什么 原来只是这些吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.86,0:05:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你认为我还会谅解你和葵现在的关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.53,0:05:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真让我吃惊得说不出话来 你这个背信弃义的家伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你竟然逃避了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.64,0:05:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你背叛了信任着作为婚约者的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.37,0:05:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而不懈努力的女儿的心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.38,0:05:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,背叛了疼爱这个女儿的我们的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.15,0:05:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说有话要谈 还以为你准备谢罪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.05,0:06:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没有打算要把女儿交给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.19,0:06:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了的话 现在就给我立刻滚出去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.53,0:06:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父亲大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.63,0:06:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我确实违反了约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.13,0:06:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能称不上是婚约者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.87,0:06:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能得不到原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.47,0:06:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 我已经不想再逃避了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.81,0:06:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是为了小葵…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.48,0:06:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了葵…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.22,0:06:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱少爷是个温柔的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.42,0:06:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且很坚强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.76,0:06:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那一定是因为比任何人 都清楚什么是内心的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.87,0:06:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没有家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.04,0:06:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为母亲不适合花菱家这个理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.64,0:06:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我父母的结婚并没有得到承认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.61,0:07:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并且 母亲带着刚出生的我 和父亲被拆散了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.22,0:07:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 我的父亲由于事故死后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.36,0:07:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱家为了得到继承者强行把我接入家族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.86,0:07:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时 我又被迫与唯一的亲人—母亲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.93,0:07:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我对花菱家没有感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.14,0:07:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只希望有一天能够与母亲重聚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.47,0:07:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是终究无法重聚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.49,0:07:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从那以后 我就一直孤单一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.86,0:07:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有可依靠的人 没有可会的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.70,0:07:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寂寞 悲哀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.17,0:07:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种感受 失去家人的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.77,0:08:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想让小葵体验到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.94,0:08:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以来到这里 想好好地谈一谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.65,0:08:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰少爷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.62,0:08:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说完了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.99,0:08:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以为用这种话就能得到原谅吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.26,0:08:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是个愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.00,0:08:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父亲大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.16,0:08:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父亲大人 请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.33,0:08:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵、樱庭葵对我来说 是不可缺少的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.67,0:08:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想再失去所爱的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.89,0:08:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.66,0:08:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.51,0:09:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰少爷 葵 没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.45,0:09:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父亲已经承认了薰少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.52,0:09:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夫人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.35,0:09:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以父亲并没有赶走薰少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.82,0:09:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是自己走出了房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.02,0:09:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.89,0:09:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟大哥哥在一起时 千夏非常安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.13,0:10:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不高兴的事全都忘掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.65,0:10:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父亲大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.65,0:10:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请原谅我刚才的无礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.86,0:10:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜欢你的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.30,0:10:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是你回来以后 一次都没笑过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.47,0:10:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在你出生的那天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.98,0:10:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天空是能一眼看穿似的蓝天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.21,0:10:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像今天一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.65,0:10:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蓝色是一种能抚慰人的心灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.05,0:10:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,温柔而又洁净的颜色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.52,0:11:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的名字包含了这个意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.89,0:11:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我并不是原谅了那个男的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.53,0:11:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是希望你能够一直有笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.20,0:11:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为你是我的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.91,0:11:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比生命更重要的我的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.48,0:11:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父亲大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.55,0:11:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是你的家 什么时候都可以回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.92,0:11:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢 谢谢 父亲大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.43,0:11:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太好了 葵小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.03,0:11:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿雅 这次给你添了许多麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.10,0:11:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请把头抬起来 我只是做了应该做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.98,0:11:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰少爷 葵小姐就拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.78,0:11:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿雅？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.15,0:11:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.38,0:12:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的任务已经完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.82,0:12:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.09,0:12:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有许多照顾不周的地方 还请原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.26,0:12:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愿你与薰少爷永远幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.93,0:12:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿雅小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.60,0:12:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起回去吧 阿雅 回到我们家人的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.21,0:12:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都等着我们回去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.38,0:12:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么？为什么准备晚会？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.42,0:12:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有大哥哥他们的联系了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.16,0:12:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.83,0:12:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.43,0:12:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果今天也不回来的话 菜都会浪费了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.50,0:12:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊 完全是乱来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.50,0:12:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.00,0:12:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这些小事就不要管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.34,0:12:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那到底是为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.28,0:13:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说不准今天就会回来 不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.71,0:13:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了什么时候回来都可以准备好饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.55,0:13:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回来后用微笑迎接 这就是所谓的家人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.65,0:13:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,家人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.43,0:13:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不明白吗 也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.16,0:13:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 在这里住下的话 就会明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.67,0:13:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.94,0:13:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住下的话？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.84,0:13:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.17,0:13:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.18,0:13:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.28,0:13:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.28,0:13:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欢迎回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.83,0:13:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暖洋洋的 感觉真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.90,0:13:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.00,0:14:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上课时也睡得很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.60,0:14:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多亏如此现在精神十足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.27,0:14:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请不要这样 蒂娜学长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.28,0:14:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话说回来 小繭 准备跟到什么时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.95,0:14:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天繭被邀请去薰少爷家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.82,0:14:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天？你不是每天都去玩的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.66,0:14:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是偶尔而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.99,0:14:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大多是没被邀请 不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.60,0:14:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是由繭来决定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.40,0:14:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歪理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.41,0:14:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看 钿女可是欢迎我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.68,0:14:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钿女 你这个叛徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.25,0:14:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钿女已经跟繭小姐很熟悉了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.75,0:14:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然 这可是射人先射马之计啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.72,0:14:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家回来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.29,0:14:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵 我回…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.29,0:14:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦 花菱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.06,0:14:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好慢呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.23,0:15:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,铃木 佐藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.93,0:15:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在干什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.17,0:15:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是搬家呀 搬家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.60,0:15:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搬家？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.74,0:15:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道 你们也搬到这里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？你在说什么呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.01,0:15:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要误会了 花菱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.61,0:15:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 睡着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.95,0:15:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.45,0:15:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你醒了吗？千夏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.62,0:15:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.46,0:15:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你趁乱干什么啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.29,0:15:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏可以原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.79,0:15:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繭可不原谅啊！快放开…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.80,0:15:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.64,0:15:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从今天开始 千夏将入住这幢房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.24,0:15:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.67,0:15:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么说来 曾说过考进了这里的高中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.48,0:15:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从现在开始每天 都会在一起了呀 大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.91,0:15:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看啊 这就是千夏上的高中的校服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.99,0:15:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想让哥哥看看 就穿着来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.46,0:16:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么 繭也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.73,0:16:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱少爷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.06,0:16:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你想勾引吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.56,0:16:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.67,0:16:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉唉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.23,0:16:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 放开他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.97,0:16:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰少爷 野人用暴力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.91,0:16:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,野人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.41,0:16:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…千夏被压在下面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.75,0:16:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.82,0:16:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让开 大家让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.46,0:16:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干杯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.86,0:16:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏 再说一次：请多关照！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.86,0:16:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要请教你许多东西哦 蒂娜姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.03,0:16:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么不明白的尽管问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.64,0:16:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论什么我都可以教你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.87,0:16:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了学习吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.31,0:16:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.24,0:16:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？你对我这个受到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.74,0:16:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正式邀请的客人 有什么意见吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.65,0:17:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理员小姐 请你好好说说 那个乱来的小鬼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.95,0:17:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要揉胸口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.79,0:17:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不、不好 无意中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.19,0:17:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么无意中 蒂娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.13,0:17:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 管理员小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.56,0:17:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜学长真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.23,0:17:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是可悲的本能啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.47,0:17:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫西园寺琉伽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.04,0:17:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你、你好 初次见面 我叫水无月千夏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.26,0:17:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夜樱真美啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.79,0:17:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.26,0:17:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,星星也非常漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.30,0:17:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.27,0:17:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个 小葵 看着我的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.20,0:17:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,樱花和星星都看不见了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.71,0:18:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系 因为现在只想好好看着薰少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.38,0:18:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是、是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.65,0:18:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小、小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.98,0:18:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对、对不起 很难受吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.19,0:18:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 那个…不是难受 感觉很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.43,0:18:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌 薰少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.63,0:18:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.86,0:18:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 好想再来一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.10,0:18:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真想再来一次啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.70,0:18:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰、薰少爷 请不要用这种眼神看我
